{"id": 57721, "date": "2025-07-13T04:00:09", "date_gmt": "2025-07-13T11:00:09", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57721"}, "modified": "2026-03-02T15:42:54", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-02T23:42:54", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-13-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/13/kingdom-of-days-july-13-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 13"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce headlines two shows at the Bottom Line in New York City. By this time, recording sessions are underway for <em>Born to Run</em>, and Bruce has been writing prolifically. These shows feature work-in-progress versions of &#8220;Jungleland&#8221; and &#8220;Born to Run&#8221; and are fascinating to listen to.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ICJr6lSGS3c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JJEmPVFAvM8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yh2oBFsFfgA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>In a stroke of last-minute inspiration, Steven Van Zandt arranges a horn section for &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out.&#8221; Randy and Michael Brecker provide the wind-power, completing the song mere weeks before its official release.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LOkQsVJV8ts?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band complete &#8220;Mary Lou&#8221; at the Power Station in New York City. It will remain in the vault for almost two decades.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/h1nEWj7QVDY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band kick off a five-night stand at The Spectrum in Philadelphia.</p>\n<div id=\"v-FHiJ0uH9-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/FHiJ0uH9?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3005\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-0713/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?fit=837%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"837,1024\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1379847263&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-0713\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?fit=245%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?fit=758%2C927&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3005 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?resize=758%2C927&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"927\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?w=837&amp;ssl=1 837w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?resize=245%2C300&amp;ssl=1 245w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0713.jpg?resize=768%2C940&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19520\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-07-13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?fit=1138%2C957&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1138,957\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593374686&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-13\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?fit=300%2C252&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?fit=758%2C637&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19520 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?resize=758%2C637&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"637\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?w=1138&amp;ssl=1 1138w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?resize=300%2C252&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?resize=1024%2C861&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1981-07-13.jpg?resize=768%2C646&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play their second of two nights in East Troy, Wisconsin.</p>\n<div id=\"v-gnhXXMxQ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/gnhXXMxQ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/P3JL1L83yGA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zAPub4sGssMzCSJ3s27LlyR\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19521\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?fit=1255%2C697&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1255,697\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593374878&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-13\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?fit=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?fit=758%2C421&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19521 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?resize=758%2C421&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?w=1255&amp;ssl=1 1255w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?resize=1024%2C569&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1984-07-13.jpg?resize=768%2C427&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new band wrap up the European leg of World Tour 1992 with a fifth and final show at Wembley Arena. &#8220;Prove It All Night&#8221; makes its tour debut, and &#8220;Born in the U.S.A.&#8221; is dropped from the set list for the first time since its debut in 1984.</p>\n<div id=\"v-pbxCty6f-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/pbxCty6f?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1993:\u00a0</strong>Patti Scialfa releases her first solo album,\u00a0<em>Rumble Doll,\u00a0</em>along with &#8220;Lucky Girl,&#8221; the lead-off single and video. Listen to Patti&#8217;s promotional radio interview and performance below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-J5occ_FqcA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zDFajspQd38?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19522\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1993-07-13a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?fit=788%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"788,961\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593375114&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1993-07-13a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?fit=246%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?fit=758%2C924&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19522 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?resize=758%2C924&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"924\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?w=788&amp;ssl=1 788w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?resize=246%2C300&amp;ssl=1 246w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1993-07-13a.jpg?resize=768%2C937&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"35865\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1993-07-13b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?fit=495%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"495,961\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593375130&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1993-07-13b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?fit=155%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?fit=495%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-35865 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?resize=495%2C961&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"961\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?w=495&amp;ssl=1 495w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1993-07-13b.jpg?resize=155%2C300&amp;ssl=1 155w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings his Devils &amp; Dust acoustic tour back to North America, kicking off with a show at Corel Center in Ottawa. Bruce plays a fairly standard set, but a lightning strike-induced power outage at the end of &#8220;Reno&#8221; provides some unplanned excitement.</p>\n<div id=\"v-LRnkEQ4z-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/LRnkEQ4z?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28253\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2005-07-13-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-13.jpg?fit=557